docs.title: Kobra Go Mods
docs.text: This is a collection of all my modifications that I have made to my Kobra Go 3D printer. The goal of this repo is to track changes, have useful tutorials, and continually update my experience with this machine.

docs.title: Twitchyfin
docs.text: A twitch vod downloader and sorter, akin to JellyFin. This project is in extremely early development stages and will be continued at some point (tm).

docs.title: Data Analytics
docs.text: Currently developed for internal use at my company, this software may at one point see the light of day. Once stripped of all its sensitive aspects, anyway.
